---
By: Tapovan Maharaj
Locus:
  Page: 176
  Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Friendship
---
All people in the world are not friends to all other people. Some people
who pose as friends prove to be no friends at all in the hour of need. But
he who sees the Self in all, has no desires of his own whatsoever, is the
friend of all, at all times, and in all circumstances.
